  "title": "5 days Indoor Sales Coordinator up to $3000 (Clementi)",
  "description": "<p>Indoor Sales Coordinator</p><p>Working Hours: 9am – 6:30pm (Mon–Fri)</p><p>Salary: $2,000 – $3,000</p><p>Location: Clementi</p><p>Job Scope:</p><ul><li>Handle customer inquiries, prepare quotations, and process orders accurately.</li><li>Coordinate with kitchen and operations teams for smooth order fulfillment and timely delivery.</li><li>Maintain relationships with existing clients and follow up on new leads.</li><li>Provide product recommendations and catering solutions based on customer needs.</li><li>Manage customer feedback to ensure high service satisfaction.</li><li>Maintain sales documentation and perform daily administrative tasks.</li><li>Support marketing and event activities as needed.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>O Level / Diploma / Degree in Business, Marketing, or related field.</li><li>Minimum 1 year relevant experience in F&B or catering preferred.</li><li>Self-disciplined, proactive, and detail-oriented with strong sense of urgency.</li><li>Creative, dynamic, and sales-oriented with good problem-solving skills.</li><li>Outgoing, highly motivated, able to work independently and in a team.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Company Name: Talent Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 24C2338</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Loke Sai Lye (Loke)</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24123366</p><p>Email: loke.dexter@talentrecruitmentsg.com</p><p>Contact Number: 8168 8648</p>",
